   <S PAR='1' RSNT='1' SNO='1'>PREFACE</S>
   <S PAR='2' RSNT='1' SNO='2'>Volume 53 of The Collected Works, The Ministry of God's Word, contains eighteen lessons given by Watchman Nee to his co-workers in a training at Kuling between 1948 and 1949.</S>
   <S PAR='3' RSNT='1' SNO='3'>The chapters are divided into four sections.</S>
   <S PAR='4' RSNT='1' SNO='4'>The main subject is the ministers of God's word and their ministry.</S>
   <S PAR='5' RSNT='1' SNO='5'>The structure and divisions of the book are well organized, and the content is rich and unique.</S>
   <S PAR='6' RSNT='1' SNO='6'>May the Lord bless the reader with the light and revelation contained in these pages.</S>
   </TEXT>
